blocks.subject: FW: FW: NOTARIAL CERTIFICATE FOR ENRON CORP.
text: Louise, I have just sent an email to follow up with Steve Irvin and Jaime Williams to obtain their pre-ranking clusters on their direct reports.  I will need to obtain your pre-ranking for both Steve and Jaime as well. Let me know your thoughts and I will gladly enter it into the PEP system.
